data.name: قاصدک
data.description: What started out in 2012 as a one–man–show has become a team of web designers, web developers, graphic designers and digital marketers working to generate results for clients in Iran and around the world. Qasedak GP is a full–service design agency with a focus on Graphic Design, Web Design & Development, WordPress Website Design, Search Engine Optimization (SEO) and Social Media and  Digital Marketing
